libsphinxclient (2.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Support string attributes and 64bit multi-attributes.
  * Add newest ranking modes except.
  * Remove support for sphinx search older than 0.9.9.
  * Rewrite SearchConfig_t interface to use dptr.

