libsphinxclient (2.0.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Binary incompatible, new version of debian package
  * Obvious unnecessary things removed from public interface (filter data)
  * Added configurable support for connection retry
  * All networking handled newly by new layer QueryMachine_t (polling state
    machine)

